comments: Porzingis (BOS) legally contests Bane's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Holiday (BOS) establishes himself in Williams' (MEM) path and does not deliver illegal contact as the pick is set.
Porzingis (BOS) does not move his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
While defending the shot, Aldama (MEM) grabs Porzingis' (BOS) jersey, which affects his post shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) firms up over his right foot in Holiday's (BOS) path and marginal side-to-side contact occurs during the pick.
White (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Bane (MEM) prior to incidental arm contact occurring during the drive.
Aldama (MEM) inbounds the ball in under 5 seconds.
Porzingis (BOS) is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
While defending White's (BOS) drive, Bane (MEM) get his hand on the ball and a jump ball is correctly whistled.
Bane (MEM) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) jumps alongside Holiday (BOS) and avoids making arm contact during Holiday's dunk attempt.
Holiday (BOS) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Aldama's (MEM) arm.
Porzingis (BOS) cleanly blocks and legally contests Williams' (MEM) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
